HEADWORD: Porrect
<hw>Por*rect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>porrectus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>porrigere</ets> to stretch out
before one's self, to but forth.]</ety> <def>Extended horizontally;
stretched out.</def>⟦br⟧
